Get and build Python 3.12 from source

    sudo apt update
    sudo apt install build-essential zlib1g-dev libncurses5-dev libgdbm-dev libnss3-dev libssl-dev libreadline-dev libffi-dev libsqlite3-dev
    wget https://python.org/ftp/python/3.12.1/Python-3.12.1.tgz
    tar -xf Python-3.12.1.tgz 
    cd Python-3.12.1
    ./configure --enable-optimizations
    sudo make altinstall

Build a Python virtual env
    
    python3.12 -m venv .venv
    . .venv/bin/activate
    pip install -r requirements.txt

Run the dht sensor listener
    
    python -m src.listener

Run the flask server
    
    flask --app src/server run --host 0.0.0.0
    
